item.title: Prayer bpn12417 in Namibia
item.description: Lidina lyoye ndyo liveruro lyande, Hompa wande, ano livhuruko kukoye mutondo wande. Pepi nove ndyo lihuguvaro lyande, shihoro shakukoye ndje ghunyande. Nkenda yoye kukwande liveruro lyande nalipameko lyande mughudjuni ghuno nka namughudjuni ogho ghuna ku yo. Vyashiri, ove, Mutapiwanavintje, Muyivinavintje, Mukonentuwanavintje. (Source category: Rugciriku : LIVERURO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12417)
